## Protocol

- One entry per Work Order
- Update status immediately when WO state changes
- Plan acceptance should move the WO to `Accepted - Awaiting Entry Audit`, not directly to implementation
- Update the `Audit Loop` column whenever a checkpoint completes or blocks progress
- Move to Completed with date when all phases done and gates pass
- This is the **single source of truth** for WO tracking
